    "Sukkur and Larkana summers are extreme — temperatures regularly exceed 48°C, making SEPCO one of the highest-consumption DISCOs in summer. Inverter ACs and proper insulation are essential investments.",
    "Khairpur date farm owners using SEPCO: solar irrigation pumps offer massive savings for agricultural water needs in this sun-drenched region with some of Pakistan's highest irradiance.",
    "Avoid running electric fans continuously in closed rooms. Cross-ventilation with strategically opened windows reduces the cooling load on ACs and fans combined.",
    "Use LED lighting throughout. Sukkur and Ghotki residential areas with long summer evenings and extended lighting hours benefit enormously from LED efficiency.",
    "Apply for SEPCO net metering. Upper Sindh receives exceptionally high solar irradiance year-round. Sukkur has some of the best solar generation conditions in Pakistan.",
